{"title":"新民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么阶级说什么话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么藤结什么瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么树开什么花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么时代爱什么人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么阶级说什么话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔上海“街头文艺”〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盏红灯高空照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心蹦蹦跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳得砖墙随风长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼烟囱入云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心啊心啊为啥跳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨，总路线公布了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔齐齐哈尔“诗传单”〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新信天游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进歌儿唱一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大瓮小瓮不空闲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进歌儿唱两年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大囤儿流小囤满；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进歌儿唱三年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食堆得像高山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进歌儿唱十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食堆堆超过山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈高山不能比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食堆堆堆上天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔西安“总路线诗传单”〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气翻过万重山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄一齐登高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懒汉才坐下水船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人听了总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气翻过万重山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺喜把笔都写烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲锣把手也打酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皆因有了总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报多得堆上天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔重庆“红岩”月刊附页〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四千五千在后边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去小麦不过百，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说种麦合不来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前年三百是特等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个农民喜开怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年千斤真稀罕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说产量顶破天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年单产3215，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细想还是有缺点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地没整好草少薅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说明产量没到边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年再鼓一把劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四千五千在后边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔武汉“长江文艺”月刊附页〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}